title: Girlfriend Photo Editor&Frames

creator: Vexill Studios
descriptionHtml:
A girlfriend is a female companion. Who supports you in ups and downs and in some other things too. A girlfriend is a girl who travels with you for outings, movies, restaurants, etc… who gives you company for your life journey.

Girlfriends may share all the things with you. When she is with you might feel that you are a very lucky and happiest person in the world, and feel like going out with her spending a good time.
Having a girlfriend is a kind of feeling in your heart. This might be missing something in your life when she is not with you and your girlfriend must be very special and unique in your life.


How to use:

❖ Take a selfie or capture a photo with your camera or select photos from the gallery. This girlfriend photo frames app has a full image crop option. Unwanted background can be removed by eraser.

❖ Background can be changed with beautiful images. Select and apply any stickers from the list in this girlfriend photo editor & frames app and drag it to the right position, rotate it, multi-touch to resize it, and fit on your pic.

❖ Stickers and images both have flip functionality in this girlfriend app. Photo color effects will make your pics colorful & beautiful. You can add text on the image as per your choice with different font styles and colors in this flight photo editor.

❖ The final edited image can be set as wallpaper of your device. You can save the final image and share it with your friends or girlfriends on all social media networks from this sea app.
